readable.content: A brown dog is jumping after a tennis ball . A brown dog leaps into the air to catch a dirty tennis ball in its mouth . A dog that looks much like a coyote jumps into the air over a grassy field to catch a tennis ball . A red dog jumps to catch a tennis ball in the dry tall grass . The brown dog catches a ball in the air .
